[PROBLEM] : Get a string from the user and find the sum of numbers in the string.
Input : Hello56 Output : 11

SOLUTION [JAVA]

class HelloWorld {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String str="dfg056";
        int add=0;
        char[] arr = str.toCharArray();
        for(char c : arr)
        {
            if(Character.isDigit(c))
            {
                int num=c-48;
                add=add+num;
            }
        }
        System.out.println(add);
    }
}
